theorem Topology.dense_iff_interiorClosure_eq_univ
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    Dense (A : Set X) ↔
      interior (closure (A : Set X)) = (Set.univ : Set X) := by
  constructor
  · intro hDense
    exact interior_closure_eq_univ_of_dense (A := A) hDense
  · intro hInt
    have h_subset : (Set.univ : Set X) ⊆ closure (A : Set X) := by
      -- `interior (closure A) ⊆ closure A`, and by `hInt` the left side is `univ`.
      have h : interior (closure (A : Set X)) ⊆ closure (A : Set X) :=
        interior_subset
      simpa [hInt] using h
    have h_closure : closure (A : Set X) = (Set.univ : Set X) :=
      Set.Subset.antisymm (Set.subset_univ _) h_subset
    simpa [Dense] using h_closure

theorem Topology.closure_subset_univ {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    closure (A : Set X) ⊆ (Set.univ : Set X) := by
  intro x _
  trivial
